{
    "text": "My friend the bear",
    "created": "Sat, 17 Sep 2022 19:07:02 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "image": "http://wirehose.com/images/blog/dall-e-my-friend-the-bear.png",
    "metaimage": "http://wirehose.com/images/blog/dall-e-my-friend-the-bear.png",
    "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "(1 min read • Illustration by DALL-E)",
            "created": "Sat, 17 Sep 2022 19:07:19 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#a190719"
        },
        {
            "text": "",
            "created": "Sat, 17 Sep 2022 19:07:20 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#a190720"
        },
        {
            "text": "Just the other day, not so far away from right here, there was a little boy who got lost in the woods. But he wasn’t scared, because a BEAR saved him! This really happened. Everybody was talking about it. A little boy, saved by a bear.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "Now, some time after the boy was saved by a bear, everybody had moved on to other amazing stories about bears and what not. And they forgot about the boy who was saved by a bear.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "But the boy never forgot, of course. He thought about his friend the bear every single day!",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "When the refrigerator door was left open and all the ice cream melted, that bear saved that little boy again.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "When the little boy couldn’t find his jacket and they were running late, the bear once again saved the boy.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "At the zoo, the bear saved the boy, wrestling an elephant before the boy could get trampled!",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "Stuck in a tree? Not with that bear around. And when the boy threw a ball up on the roof, who climbed up and saved that boy? That’s right, the bear.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "Several times, that bear saved the boy by fixing the internet.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "Saved from a math test? Boy plus bear equals A-plus.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "(The bear also saved the boy by hacking the security cameras during a heist, but that was years and years later, and really none of our concern right now.)",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "But the boy most often appreciated when the bear would save him from another bath.",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/190702.html?title=myFriendTheBear#aNaNNaNNaN"
        }
    ]
}

