{
    "text": "as yet untitled",
    "created": "Sat, 17 Sep 2022 21:53:36 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "Oh, the drunken pheasants!",
            "created": "Sat, 17 Sep 2022 21:53:56 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#a215356"
        },
        {
            "text": "I would like to fill the pockets of my great long coat",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "with brown birds snoozing away",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "and trudge home beside him",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "boots crunching the frosty mud",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "Finally reaching the fence bordering between safe and adventure",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"A good night's work, eh?\"",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "leans and lights the pipe that he has been treasuring",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "His kind eyes, mischief and love and",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "it's been so long since i felt",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "so safe",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "so happy",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "so cold",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "Let's get some cocoa",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/PostMonsterG/2022/09/17/215336.html?title=asYetUntitled#aNaNNaNNaN"
        },
        {
            "text": "And don't tell your mother",
            "created": "Sat, 17 Sep 2022 21:55:54 GMT",
